## Quick Start (New Chat)

1. Copy `REFERENCE.md` and paste at top of chat
2. Copy relevant `/weeks/week-XXX.md` file(s) and paste
3. Ask Claude: "Ready to write?"
4. Claude writes opening, you respond, back-and-forth until scene ends

